nodes.text: Wachtor was a Victory-class Star Destroyer in the service of the Imperial Navy during the Galactic Civil War.

Wachtor is one of several names in the class-specific lists from which the video games Star Wars: Empire at War and its expansion Forces of Corruption randomly select names for capital ships. The existence of the name in this list indicates such a ship existed in the Imperial Navy at that time, but no other information is canonically available.
